        <updateDate>2009-08-05T20:21:48Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Brownfields Remediation Permanent Tax Incentive Act - Amends the Internal Revenue Code to make permanent the taxpayer election to expense (deduct in the current taxable year) expenditures for environmental remediation (i.e., abatement or control of hazardous substances at contaminated sites).<br> </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
